Fixed GPS Access
Create slight entropy in GPS latitude/longitude for each individual network sent to the server
issue.body:
Currently the GPS latitude/longitude is the same when a set of local public networks is sent to the server at the same time. This results in the the points overlapping and making it difficult to view which networks are available.

Each latitude/longitude should include a very slight randomization so the points will not completely cover each other in the Maps view.
